ew original songs! New songs include:\n\t\u2022 Against The Tide\n\t\u2022 Cabaret Carnival\n\t\u2022 Champions Creed\n\t\u2022 Chasing The Weekend\n\t\u2022 Circuit Board Queen\n\t\u2022 Cuchulainn\n\t\u2022 Digital Odyssey\n\t\u2022 Echoes In The Dark\n\t\u2022 Finding Hope\n\t\u2022 Ignite The Night\n\t\u2022 Midnight Masquerade\n\t\u2022 Neon Horizon\n\t\u2022 Rebels With A Cause\n\t\u2022 Redemption\n\t\u2022 Relevant\n\t\u2022 Ride From The Ashes\n\t\u2022 Rise Up\n\t\u2022 Ritzy Rendezvous\n\t\u2022 Shadow BoXR\n\t\u2022 Swingin Through Time\n\t\u2022 Symphony Of The Seas\n\t\u2022 The Awakening\n\t\u2022 Thors Journey\n\t\u2022 Watch Me Rise\n\t\u2022 Wild And Free\n\n2) Added two new GameMode overrides! Target Speed Mod and Song Speed Mod! Like the other settings in this window, it is a saved setting and will be saved to your playlists and your default settings when playing a single song.\n\t\u2022 Target Speed Mod: Players can now add a modifier to the speed of the targets. \n\t\u2022 Song Speed Mod: Players can now add a modifier to the speed of the actual song changing the song length, pitch, and BPM. \n\n3) Choreography Improvements.\n\t\u2022 If the difficulty is set to Easy or Normal, targets will no longer appear under obstacles. They will still appear sometimes appear under obstacles in Hard and Expert difficulties.\n\t\u2022 Obstacles will appear a little more frequently now.\n\n4) Improved Timing Display:\n\t\u2022 New and improved timing display added to targets to help guide your timing! The timing display can be enable or disabled in the Player Settings tab of the settings menu.\n\n5) Bug Fixes:\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing an error to be thrown sometimes when returning to main menu before a song completes.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing targets to appear inside of obstacles sometimes when in Jabs only mode.", "created_date": 1726594767, "id": "8720469854652216", "version": "0.2.0", "version_code": 76, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPRO